src_enUS: You’ve hit Level 15—great work! Now’s the perfect time to supercharge your progress. With the Deluxe Edition, you’ll unlock 11 Ascension Passes, guaranteeing you exclusive goodies and faster leveling for each individual god.
Hit Level 15? Get 11 Passes with Deluxe Founder's!
